apnapan is a 1977 indian bollywood drama film produced & directed by j. om prakash on filmyug pvt ltd banner .   starring reena roy , sanjeev kumar , jeetendra , sulakshana pandit in lead roles and music composed by laxmikant pyarelal .   the film recorded as hit at box office .   reena roy played selfish gold-digger that abandons her husband and child , won her numerous accolades and a filmfare award for best supporting actress .   however , she rejected the award on the basis that she is the heroine of the film , not the supporting actress .   this is precursor to the type of role meryl streep played two years later in " kramer vs kramer " .   this film is remade in telugu as illalu ( 1981 ) starring shoban babu , sridevi , jayasudha in pivotal roles .